                    "line_text": "Remettre entre vos mains les rênes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "D'un empire à vos lois soumis.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Reconnaissant et plein de zèle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Que n'ai-je su, comme eux fidèle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Acquitter ce que j'ai promis !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Du milieu d'un brillant nuage\nVous voyez les humbles mortels\nVous rendre à l'envi leur hommage,\nProsternés devant vos autels ;\nEt les puissances souveraines\nRemettre entre vos mains les rênes\nD'un empire à vos lois soumis.\nReconnaissant et plein de zèle,\nQue n'ai-je su, comme eux fidèle,\nAcquitter ce que j'ai promis !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Mais, hélas ! que ma conscience",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "M'offre un souvenir douloureux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Une coupable indifférence",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "M'a pu faire oublier mes vœux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Confus, j'en entends le murmure.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Malheureux ! je suis donc parjure !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Mais non ; fidèle désormais,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Je jure ces autels antiques,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Parés de vos saintes reliques,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "D'accomplir les vœux que j'ai faits.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais, hélas ! que ma conscience\nM'offre un souvenir douloureux !\nUne coupable indifférence\nM'a pu faire oublier mes vœux.\nConfus, j'en entends le murmure.\nMalheureux ! je suis donc parjure !\nMais non ; fidèle désormais,\nJe jure ces autels antiques,\nParés de vos saintes reliques,\nD'accomplir les vœux que j'ai faits."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Vous, tombeau sacré que j'honore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Enrichi des dons de nos rois,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Et vous, bergère que j'implore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Écoutez ma timide voix.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Pardonnez à mon impuissance,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Si ma faible reconnaissance",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Ne peut égaler vos faveurs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Dieu même, à contenter facile,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Ne croit point l'offrande trop vile",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Que nous lui faisons de nos cœurs.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vous, tombeau sacré que j'honore,\nEnrichi des dons de nos rois,\nEt vous, bergère que j'implore,\nÉcoutez ma timide voix.\nPardonnez à mon impuissance,\nSi ma faible reconnaissance\nNe peut égaler vos faveurs.\nDieu même, à contenter facile,\nNe croit point l'offrande trop vile\nQue nous lui faisons de nos cœurs."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Les Indes, pour moi trop avares,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Font couler l'or en d'autres mains :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Je n'ai point de ces meubles rares",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Qui flattent l'orgueil des humains.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Loin d'une fortune opulente,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Aux trésors que je vous présente",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Ma seule ardeur donne du prix ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Et si cette ardeur peut vous plaire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Agréez que j'ose vous faire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Un hommage de mes écrits.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les Indes, pour moi trop avares,\nFont couler l'or en d'autres mains :\nJe n'ai point de ces meubles rares\nQui flattent l'orgueil des humains.\nLoin d'une fortune opulente,\nAux trésors que je vous présente\nMa seule ardeur donne du prix ;\nEt si cette ardeur peut vous plaire,\nAgréez que j'ose vous faire\nUn hommage de mes écrits."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Eh quoi ! puis-je dans le silence",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Ensevelir ces nobles noms",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "De protectrice de la France",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Et de ferme appui des Bourbons ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Jadis nos campagnes arides,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Trompant nos attentes timides,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Vous durent leur fertilité ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Et, par votre seule prière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Vous désarmâtes la colère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Du ciel contre nous irrité.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh quoi ! puis-je dans le silence\nEnsevelir ces nobles noms\nDe protectrice de la France\nEt de ferme appui des Bourbons ?\nJadis nos campagnes arides,\nTrompant nos attentes timides,\nVous durent leur fertilité ;\nEt, par votre seule prière,\nVous désarmâtes la colère\nDu ciel contre nous irrité."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "La Mort même, à votre présence,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
